tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  date_submitted TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE surveys (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    survey_questions TEXT,
    survey_date DATE,
    survey_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE patient_feedback (
  feedback_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date TIMESTAMP,
  helpfulness_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE patient_surveys (
  survey_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  survey_question TEXT,
  survey_response TEXT,
  survey_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE program_feedback (
  feedback_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date TIMESTAMP,
  effectiveness_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50),
  patient_age INT,
  patient_gender VARCHAR(10),
  patient_contact VARCHAR(15)
)

CREATE TABLE Surveys (
  survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_name VARCHAR(50),
  survey_description TEXT,
  survey_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE Programs (
  program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(50),
  program_description TEXT,
  program_duration INT
)

CREATE TABLE Responses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  response_text TEXT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP
)
